transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Ha ji.
Customer: Hello
Executive: Ha ji. Haan sir Vikrant Kumar bol raha hun India Mart se.
Customer: Vikrant ji bol rahe hain. Haan.
Executive: Theek hai sir. Sir, kaafi time se aapko kaafi time sir aapko call kar raha tha.
Customer: Haan sir?
Executive: Kaafi time sir aapko call kar raha tha aap receive nahi kar rahe the.
Customer: Haan haan haan. Kaam mere ko yaad nahi hai ki kaun the.
Executive: Kal aapke father ji se bhi baat hui thi.
Customer: Kisse baat kar rahe hain sir aap?
Executive: Kya sir?
Customer: Aap kisse baat kar rahe hain?
Executive: Ek minute sir main aapko back call karta hun. Back call karke phir aapko batata hun, theek hai? Catalog open kar lun aapka.
